{{Navbox/Spookality}}
'''Spookality''' is an annual Halloween-themed event. It consists of an [[Avatars|avatar]] and [[Worlds|world]] jam. Winners of the jam receive prizes and have their creations showcased within [[VRChat]].

==Jams==
[[File:{{#setmainimage:Spookality_2025_FORMAT.webp}}|thumb|Spookality 2025 key art]]
The jams hosted during Spookality allow creators to show off their best Halloween-themed avatars and worlds. The jams also highly encourage creators to make their creations [[cross-platform]], some themes make this a requirement.

==Prizes==
Winners of the jam also receive prizes. Usually it consists of your creation being showcased within the [[VRChat Home]], Spookality Hub, or a world row. Sometimes, you can win IRL prizes such as, [[Merch|VRChat Merch]], or VR hardware.

